data.actual_result: Not Only is the command to send the emote copied, but also a bunch of numbers are copied along side it preventing it to be re sent without removing the code
data.expected_result: Only the command to send the emote is copied
data.short_description: When copying an emote, it also copies code/ an ID.
data.steps_to_repro: - Send an emote, and send it without text - Copy the emote, as you would do with any other piece of text - When pasting you will see that not only has the command to send emote been copied, numbers are jumbled -
